=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F11%2F025603_f71f854c9629bb3d959b71cc2f5494a1.jpg&h=42b2c38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇方法斷尾<br />\n點解要痕係春袋<br />\n點忍得住<br />\n一得又被人話變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71312d2a18eb202dbf34bff40871a48371eadb4d","tid":31691,"uid":36753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留明<br />\nI<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/11/025603_f71f854c9629bb3d959b71cc2f5494a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F11%2F025603_f71f854c9629bb3d959b71cc2f5494a1.jpg&h=42b2c38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇方法斷尾<br />\n點解要痕係春袋<br />\n點忍得住<br />\n一得又被人話變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我春袋又冇事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1a7c47dc34a4ce9d73edb54dadf4e76f94645d","tid":31691,"uid":20708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:03:04.000Z","msg":"中三到依加無再番發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算有都係發兩日就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfd33002352411a67ab90666e48c4f2a1ad097e","tid":31691,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>btw<br />\n樓主男人老狗 改埋啲咁嘅名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食開萬事發藍苺8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食煙好似都會有少少影響 唔知係我心理問題定點<br />\n食完會痕D<br />\n不過我唔理照食"},{"pid":"f26d1d7918bad79e34d8086f7345d39cc17c7fc2","tid":31691,"uid":63046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人有偏頭痛？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有冇關係？ 我頭痛左18年了 真係好辛苦 最近大腿又發返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51896fd4786c91704d7a6946142266f781ccfe33","tid":31691,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:18:03.000Z","msg":"6年半前確診紅斑狼瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab046105b065280556394df90cb894898c08c7de","tid":31691,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留明<br />\nI<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/11/025603_f71f854c9629bb3d959b71cc2f5494a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F11%2F025603_f71f854c9629bb3d959b71cc2f5494a1.jpg&h=42b2c38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇方法斷尾<br />\n點解要痕係春袋<br />\n點忍得住<br />\n一得又被人話變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我春袋又冇事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你無事<br />\n我有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eadb0e39171ab344f95852f273916360326c2f2f","tid":31691,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有得驗乜野食物過敏架喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未得閒驗住 係咪跟住唔食真係有用？</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n好過中醫亂叫你戒牛肉 芒果<br />\n人地真係隻隻食物同你驗<br />\n有個小朋友 本身有<br />\n驗完先知一食雞就發<br />\n雞你如果唔驗 點都唔會戒啦<br />\n<br />\n幾千蚊雖然係貴<br />\n但做人做狗自己揀"},{"pid":"6754be97e987049bf7cb46e0bd92f127d404365a","tid":31691,"uid":42199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"聽講濕疹 牛皮癬 都你免疫系統排斥 如果想斷尾可以試下食通常人地換完器官既抗排斥藥 但係抗排斥藥一般公立醫院唔會開要睇私家 同埋食果時會對腎功能有影響 食果排驗住血咁食-資料來源：牛醫生與狗護士"}]}